<list title="HEAP">
 <bullet>Not transaction-capable</bullet>
 <bullet>Stored in memory (so data lost on shutdown)</bullet>
 <bullet>Hash indexes (great for indexed lookups, not for range queries)</bullet>
 <bullet>Btree indexes in 4.1</bullet>
</list>

<list title="Dynamic">
 <bullet>Not transaction-capable</bullet>
 <bullet>Migrates between memory and disk</bullet>
 <bullet>New in 4.1</bullet>
</list>

